name: Raven Lyn Corneil
description:
Raven Lyn Corneil (born January 9, 1995) is a well-known professional model, managed by Women 360 Management New York, Freedom Los Angeles, and Storm Management London. She is simply referred to as "Raven Lyn" in the industry. Her commercial work includes G-Star Raw, Adidas, and Gap.

If you like my work, a review is more than welcome! Also, follow me on Twitter or Instagram!

Looking for something... spicy? Here's my Patreon!

Also, I recently started a blog where I will gather resources and tutorials about my work here!

Hey, people of CivitAI! This is a textual inversion of Raven Lyn Corneil. She's one of my favorite models, I could not exclude her from my work! I went back to the "basics" this time: 3000 steps and 40 public images were enough. As usual: do not use the face restore.

To use it:

  • download the file and place it into stable-diffusion-webui>embeddings folder;

  • add ravlyn95 to your prompt;

  • keep the sampling steps around 25, CFG at 7 seems to work well. Best results with DPM++ 2S a Karras + Realistic Vision. Also got some good results with Deliberate (last pic). Check the gallery for some inspiration!
